data.value: Razer Huntsman Elite Opto-Mechanical Switch Gaming Keyboard – Purple Switch is Combined with a new switch design, it’s the first clicky switch that actuates and resets at the exact same point for rapid performance. Personalize settings with hybrid on-board memory and cloud storage. It Comes with an ergonomic wrist rest for long-lasting comfort. Get free shipping on orders over 2100 BDT from Vibe Gaming.Keyboard control just got a lot faster. A multi-function digital dial with three tactile media keys gives you instant access to everything from brightness to volume in seconds. All programmable and customizable through Synapse 3—so you can set your preferred configurations right at your fingertips.
